def: Of or pertaining to the chalaza.
Of or pertaining to the rachis; spinal; vertebral. Same asRhachidian.
Having the nature of vinegar; sour; unamiable.
A peculiar perforated organ of certain spiders (Ciniflonid√¶),used for spinning a special kind of silk.
A leader in heresy; the chief of a sect of heretics. Bp.Stillingfleet.
A lock or curl of hair near the ear; a lovelock. See Lovelock.
Act of disclosing or uncovering something concealed. [Obs.]Boyle.
